Description: An interactive shiny app for signal detection of infectious disease surveillance data on national level. This app allows the user to explore and investigate the signals generated and the corresponding time series. The package includes:
 - possibility for the user to upload csv or Excel file
 - data check making sure the data is in the right format
 - flexible user settings such as different outbreak detection algorithms, time periods, stratifications and filters
 - visualisation of signal detection results as bar charts, maps, tables and time series
 - possibility to generate a report with results
